{"TopicId":206866,"ForumId":24,"TopicTitle":"Forum help if you would be so kind..","CreatedByName":"Kalalicious","CreatedById":213381,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-11T21:03:56Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Kalalicious","CreatedById":213381,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-11T21:03:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello all!\u00A0 \u00A0Lurker turning commenter here, haven\u0027t even finished my 5 approved posts yet.\u00A0 But I am wondering how to use the \u0022hidden\u0022 option so you don\u0027t force a wall of text on readers if they don\u0027t want to read or see it.\u00A0 Help?\u00A0 \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-11T23:27:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWelcome!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m not sure what you mean by \u0022hidden\u0022, but we do have the Spoiler option.\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 Select your text, and then in the editor GUI, click the Eyeball.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027ll look like this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEdit:\u00A0\u00A0 Ok , maybe \u0022hidden\u0022 makes more sense now.\u00A0 \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-02-11T23:27:59Z\u0022 title=\u002202/11/2022 11:27  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 11, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by Gargamel\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Curveball Anders","CreatedById":107529,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-12T01:12:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut note that large logs and such are loaded even if they\u0027re not shown, bringing misery to users on phones and pads.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-12T02:59:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMeanwhile, welcome to the forum. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Neptunium_69","CreatedById":218699,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-12T06:09:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell Open this by taping the top of the spoiler.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nQ1:How to open a spoiler?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA1:you know it already\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nQ2:How to make a spoiler?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA2:Above the typing zone (Or the white part that your typing appears), you will see many icons. The iron that looks like a Eye is the spoiler icon\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kalalicious","CreatedById":213381,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-12T18:50:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks everyone!\u00A0 Yeah, I knew it as spoiler as well, but as you noted Gargamel, it says \u0027hidden\u0027 when posted.\u00A0 \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ECheers!\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}